                            Based on the context: talk start time:8:56 pm on 20 July, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Thanks, Melanie! It's awesome to have our own platform to be ourselves and support others' rights. Our group, 'Connected LGBTQ Activists', is made of all kinds of people investing in positive changes. We have regular meetings, plan events and campaigns, to get together and support each other.memory context: a photo of a painted sidewalk with a rainbow design on itmemory keywords: []memory tags: ['inclusive', 'diverse', 'community', 'symbolism', 'emotional']
