talk start time:7:55 pm on 9 June, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Hey Melanie! How's it going? I wanted to tell you about my school event last week. It was awesome! I talked about my transgender journey and encouraged students to get involved in the LGBTQ community. It was great to see their reactions. It made me reflect on how far I've come since I started transitioning three years ago.memory context: Speaker Caroline says : Speaker Melaniesays : Wow, Caroline, sounds like the parade was an awesome experience! It's great to see the love and support for the LGBTQ+ community. Congrats! Has this experience influenced your goals at all?memory keywords: []memory tags: ['inclusive', 'community', 'general']
