talk start time:1:14 pm on 25 May, 2023memory content: Speaker Melaniesays : That's great, Caroline! Loving the inclusivity and support. Anything you're excited for in the adoption process?memory context: Speaker Caroline says: Thanks so much, Melanie! It's beautiful! It really brings home how much love's in families - both blood and the ones we choose. I hope to build my own family and put a roof over kids who haven't had that before. For me, adoption is a way of giving back and showing love and acceptance.memory keywords: []memory tags: ['general', "support for others' achievements"]
talk start time:10:31 am on 13 October, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Thanks, Melanie! I'm stoked to start this new chapter. It's been a dream to adopt and provide a safe, loving home for kids who need it. Do you have any experience with adoption, or know anyone who's gone through the process?memory context: Speaker Carolinesays : Thanks, Melanie! I'm stoked to start this new chapter. It's been a dream to adopt and provide a safe, loving home for kids who need it. Do you have any experience with adoption, or know anyone who's gone through the process?memory keywords: []memory tags: ['general']
talk start time:1:14 pm on 25 May, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : [Image: a photography of a sign for a new arrival and an information and domestic building] Thanks, Mel! My goal is to give kids a loving home. I'm truly grateful for all the support I've got from friends and mentors. Now the hard work starts to turn my dream into a reality. And here's one of the adoption agencies I'm looking into. It's a lot to take in, but I'm feeling hopeful and optimistic.memory context: Speaker Carolinesays : Thanks, Melanie! I'll do my best to make sure these kids have a safe and loving home. I'm truly grateful for all the support I've got from friends and mentors. Now the hard work starts to turn my dream into a reality. And here's one of the adoption agencies I'm looking into. It's a lot to take in, but I'm feeling hopeful and optimistic.memory keywords: []memory tags: ['general', 'adoption', 'family']
talk start time:8:56 pm on 20 July, 2023memory content: Speaker Melaniesays : Thanks, Caroline! I'm really lucky to have my family; they bring so much joy and love.memory context: Speaker Caroline says: Thanks so much, Melanie! It's beautiful! It really brings home how much love's in families - both blood and the ones we choose. I hope to build my own family and put a roof over kids who haven't had that before. For me, adoption is a way of giving back and showing love and acceptance.memory keywords: []memory tags: ['general', 'adoption', 'family']
