talk start time:10:31 am on 13 October, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Yep! Do your research and find an adoption agency or lawyer. They'll help with the process and provide all the info. Gather documents like references, financial info and medical checks. Don't forget to prepare emotionally, since the wait can be hard. It's all worth it in the end though.memory context: Generalmemory keywords: []memory tags: []
talk start time:10:31 am on 13 October, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Hey Mel, what's up? Long time no see! I just contacted my mentor for adoption advice. I'm ready to be a mom and share my love and family. It's a great feeling. Anything new with you? Anything exciting going on?memory context: Generalmemory keywords: []memory tags: []
talk start time:9:55 am on 22 October, 2023memory content: Speaker Carolinesays : Woohoo Melanie! I passed the adoption agency interviews last Friday! I'm so excited and thankful. This is a big move towards my goal of having a family.memory context: Generalmemory keywords: []memory tags: []
